### economy-api (http://localhost:5001)

# Health Check
GET http://localhost:5001/health

###

# Get Daily Coins
POST http://localhost:5001/coin/get-daily
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "123"
}

###

# Show Coins
GET http://localhost:5001/coin/show?user_id=123

###

# Transfer Coins
POST http://localhost:5001/coin/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_user": "123",
  "to_user": "456",
  "amount": 50
}

###

# Update Coins (Admin/Manual)
PUT http://localhost:5001/coin/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "123",
  "amount": 100,
  "reason": "Bonus"
}

###

# Remove User
DELETE http://localhost:5001/coin/remove
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "123"
}

###

# Airplane Distribute
POST http://localhost:5001/airplane/distribute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "total_amount": 100,
  "participants": ["123", "456", "789"],
  "distributor": "123"
}

###

# Get Transactions
GET http://localhost:5001/transactions?user_id=123&type=transfer&limit=10

###

# Get Leaderboard
GET http://localhost:5001/leaderboard
